布节奏进行，因此一旦 Python 扩展版本（即 Python 3.8）生命周期结束，微软就会停止对它的官方支持（IT 之家注：Python 3.8 计划于 2024 年 10 月达到 EOL，因此 2025 年的第一个扩展版本将停止官方支持），而这种策略也会延用到后续版本。 据微软称，Visual Studio 的 Python 扩展适用于所有积极支持的 Python 版本。3.12 是最新版本。 去年年底，Python 指导委员会宣布了「将采用 12 个月发布周期，一年发布一个大版本」的决定。Python 语言项目团队对于新的版本开发周期规划已成定局：微软 Visual Studio Code 弃用 Python 3.7 支持，暂未删除相关代码"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/625588069"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5KvdlNf1sqZpEAMaCTEwMTI5ODc2NCCCi5ipBjAAOFBAEHIJNjI1NTg4MDY5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1697137314.822500", "card_id": "Q_624973831", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "哪种航天器推进系统，最有可能率先实现星际远航？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "这里说的「星际远航」是指航程超过 5 光年，且可以在一个人的自然寿命内完成。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-79682599f6928cedf8108e714ea60808_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/624973831"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5KvdlNf1sqZpEAMaCTEwMTE2MjI1MCDe44OpBjAAOGhAEXIJNjI0OTczODMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1697137314.822823", "card_id": "Q_274084212", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 123}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果在银河系中迷路了，怎样才能找到地球？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/274084212"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5KvdlNf1sqZpEAMaCDI